                           <div class="question-text-wrapper">
                              <span class="question-text">How to Reach Kashmir Great Lakes Trek?</span>
                              <span class="question-subheading">Everything You Need to Plan Your Trek</span>
                           </div>
                           <span class="detailfaq-icon">▼</span>
