                           <div class="detaildropdown-content">
                                                                                          <div class="detailfaq-item">
                                 <button class="detailfaq-question">
                                 <span>1. What is the Kashmir Great Lakes Trek (KGL Trek)?</span>
                                 <span class="detailfaq-icon">▼</span>
                                 </button>
                                 <div class="detailfaq-answer">
                                    <b style="" id="docs-internal-guid-f32c5375-7fff-35a7-2829-282f66bd484b"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The trek is in </span><span style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Jammu &amp; Kashmir state </span><span style="font-weight: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">, starting near </span><span style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Sonamarg </span><span style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Shitkadi Camp Himalayan hikers Camp</span><span style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> </span><span style="font-weight: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">and ending at </span><span style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Naranag</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-weight: normal;">, close to Srinagar. The </span>Kashmir Great Lakes Trek <span style="font-weight: normal;">is a breathtaking </span>trek in the Kashmir Valley<span style="font-weight: normal;">, known for its stunning alpine lakes, lush meadows, and panoramic views of snow-clad peaks. It’s considered one of </span>the most beautiful treks in India<span style="font-weight: normal;">.</span></span></b>                                 </div>
                              </div>
                                                            <div class="detailfaq-item">
                                 <button class="detailfaq-question">
                                 <span>2. What is the altitude of the trek?</span>
                                 <span class="detailfaq-icon">▼</span>
                                 </button>
                                 <div class="detailfaq-answer">
                                    The trek reaches a maximum altitude of around 13,750 ft (4,190 m).
The highest point of the trek is Gadsar Pass, which is at an altitude of approximately 
13,750 ft (4,190 meters)
.                                 </div>
                              </div>
                                                            <div class="detailfaq-item">
                                 <button class="detailfaq-question">
                                 <span>3. When is the best time to do the Kashmir Great Lakes Trek?</span>
                                 <span class="detailfaq-icon">▼</span>
                                 </button>
                                 <div class="detailfaq-answer">
                                    <p>


